data.description: Fantastic Opportunity Within Gated and Well Maintained Stonebriar at Bayside Lakes! This Beautiful Concrete Block, 5-bedroom, 4 baths, 3416 Sqft Home Built in 2019 Includes Trace Ceilings, Open Floor-plan, and 300 Sqft Covered Back Patio; Perfect Floor-plan for a Pool with Privacy of the Preserve. On the First Floor you will find the Owners Suite Inclusive of an Additional Open Room Great for Office Space, His/Her Walk-in Closets, Split Vanities &, Tub/Shower. On the First Floor on the Other Side of the Home you will find 3 Bedrooms, 2 Baths & Open Kitchen Equip with Granite, Stainless-Steel Appliances, & Double Pantries. Upstairs you will find a Bedroom, Walk-in Closet, & Full Bath with a Large Open Living Space, Great for a Game Room/Personal Studio. Community Clubhouse W/Pool and more!
